title: The J. Geils Band - Ladies Invited [320k MP3]
description:
Ladies Invited is the fifth album by American rock band The J. Geils Band, released in 1973 
 
The model for the cover artwork, illustrated by the noted fashion artist Antonio, was reportedly the actress Faye Dunaway, who married lead singer Peter Wolf the following year.
